window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>\"With a onesie, and the ability to stop time, anything is possible.\"</b></p> <p>Dragons, catgirls, guns, and magicâ€”oh, and the ability to stop time. What more could a modern gal want?</p> <p>Well... If my past would stay locked in a dark corner back on Earth, that'd be nice.</p> <p>Right, there was that one other thing: finding a way home before the world ends. But hey, that's what my mom would call the last step in your five-year plan.</p> <p>The first? Play with magic.</p>"; 
